description:
Jaan Pehechan Ho (1965) Music Video from Gumnaam

Jaan Pehechan Ho was a popular song from the 1965 movie Gumnaam which was directed by Raja Nawathe, produced by N N Sippy and starring Manoj Kumar & Nanda (actress). The music was composed by Shankar Jaikishan, with lyrics by Anand Bakshi. It was sung by Mohammed Rafi.  The song's video introduces the movie to the audiences. It was shot in a disco and features Laxmi Chhaya. The song also appears in the opening credits of the 2001 movie Ghost World.
